name: Level End Is Out Of Place
name_original: Level End Is Out Of Place
description:
This is a classic and simple platformer, where you control the ending flag!!!

It has been made in Clickteam Fusion 2.5.

It has 5 levels

It is in beta 0.1 new updates are coming in 2021 (i hope), more levels, level maker!!! And much more!!! 

The physics engine is extension to Clickteam Fusion 2.5, made by clickteam
